Package: rdviz
Type: Package
Title: Regression Discontinuity Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joe Ornstein
Maintainer: Joe Ornstein <jornstein@wustl.edu>
Description: Generates a visualization of a regression discontinuity analysis,
    including raw scatterplot, binned scatterplot, optimal bandwidths, and local polynomial fits.
